
Fonts
font-family
p{font-family: "Open Sans", Arial, sans-serif;}


font-size
p{font-size: 15px; /*absolute pixel size*/}
p{font-size: 120%; /*relative to its parent*/}
p{font-size: 1.2em; /*em: relative to the font-size on parent*/}
p{font-size: 1.2rem; /*rem: relative to the font-size on html; the root*/}


font-style
p.normal {font-style:normal;}
p.italic {font-style:italic;}
p.oblique {font-style:oblique;}


font-weight: can use 100-900 or text values like 'bold', 'bolder', 'lighter'. 400=normal, 700=bold
p.normal {font-weight:normal;}
p.thick {font-weight:bold;}
p.thicker {font-weight:900;}
